SQL_STMT_U.val:
select DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT,cast(':1' as char(10)),cast(sum(DRFT_AMOUNTCURRDRAFT) as decimal(13,2))
from :18/DRFT join :18/debc on DRFT_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO
where DRFT_DUEDATE <=':1' and DRFT_ADMNO = :19 and DRFT_CLNTNO = :20 and DRFT_DATEMONEYRECEIVED is null
group by DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT
union
select DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT,cast(':2' as char(10)),cast(sum(DRFT_AMOUNTCURRDRAFT) as decimal(13,2))
from :18/DRFT join :18/debc on DRFT_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO
where DRFT_DUEDATE between ':3'and ':2' and DRFT_ADMNO = :19 and DRFT_CLNTNO = :20 and DRFT_DATEMONEYRECEIVED is null
group by DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT
union
select DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT,cast(':4' as char(10)),cast(sum(DRFT_AMOUNTCURRDRAFT) as decimal(13,2))
from :18/DRFT join :18/debc on DRFT_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO
where DRFT_DUEDATE between ':5'and ':4' and DRFT_ADMNO = :19 and DRFT_CLNTNO = :20 and DRFT_DATEMONEYRECEIVED is null
group by DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT
union
select DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT,cast(':6' as char(10)),cast(sum(DRFT_AMOUNTCURRDRAFT) as decimal(13,2))
from :18/DRFT join :18/debc on DRFT_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO
where DRFT_DUEDATE between ':7'and ':6' and DRFT_ADMNO = :19 and DRFT_CLNTNO = :20 and DRFT_DATEMONEYRECEIVED is null
group by DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT
union
select DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT,cast(':8' as char(10)),cast(sum(DRFT_AMOUNTCURRDRAFT) as decimal(13,2))
from :18/DRFT join :18/debc on DRFT_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO
where DRFT_DUEDATE between ':9'and ':8' and DRFT_ADMNO = :19 and DRFT_CLNTNO = :20 and DRFT_DATEMONEYRECEIVED is null
group by DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT
union
select DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT,cast(':10' as char(10)),cast(sum(DRFT_AMOUNTCURRDRAFT) as decimal(13,2)) from :18/DRFT join :18/debc on DRFT_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO
where DRFT_DUEDATE between ':11'and ':10' and DRFT_ADMNO = :19 and DRFT_CLNTNO = :20 and DRFT_DATEMONEYRECEIVED is null
group by DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT
union
select DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT,cast(':12' as char(10)),cast(sum(DRFT_AMOUNTCURRDRAFT) as decimal(13,2)) from :18/DRFT join :18/debc on DRFT_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO
where DRFT_DUEDATE between ':13'and ':12' and DRFT_ADMNO = :19 and DRFT_CLNTNO = :20 and DRFT_DATEMONEYRECEIVED is null
group by DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT
union
select DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT,cast(':14' as char(10)),cast(sum(DRFT_AMOUNTCURRDRAFT) as decimal(13,2))
from :18/DRFT join :18/debc on DRFT_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO
where DRFT_DUEDATE between ':15'and ':14' and DRFT_ADMNO = :19 and DRFT_CLNTNO = :20 and DRFT_DATEMONEYRECEIVED is null
group by DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT
union
select DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT,cast(':16' as char(10)),cast(sum(DRFT_AMOUNTCURRDRAFT) as decimal(13,2))
from :18/DRFT join :18/debc on DRFT_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO
where DRFT_DUEDATE > ':17' and DRFT_ADMNO = :19 and DRFT_CLNTNO = :20 and DRFT_DATEMONEYRECEIVED is null
group by DRFT_CURRENCY,DRFT_DEBC_NO,DEBC_DEBC_SORT
order by DRFT_CURRENCY,DEBC_DEBC_SORT,3
